OL,3,CReform council leader investigated
OL,4,Cover alleged racist social media posts
OL,6,FNigel Farage has said "it doesn't look
OL,7,Fvery good" for the Reform UK leader of
OL,8,FStaffordshire County Council following
OL,9,Fclaims he posted racist remarks on
OL,10,Fsocial media.
OL,12,FCouncillor Ian Cooper was elected to
OL,13,Fthe position in May, but is now under
OL,14,Finvestigation by his party after
OL,15,Falleged racist social media posts
OL,16,Femerged.
OL,18,FThe campaign group Hope not Hate
OL,19,Fclaims racist posts online were made
OL,20,Ffrom accounts with his name.
