OL,6,FThe group said: "Reform UK's Cllr Ian
OL,7,FCooper has posted dozens of racist and
OL,8,Fbigoted posts to YouTube and X/Twitter
OL,9,Funder his personal accounts."
OL,11,FThe posts are alleged to have been
OL,12,Fmade prior to the May election - in
OL,13,FFebruary, Cooper allegedly called the
OL,14,FLondon mayor, Sadiq Khan, a
OL,15,F"narcissistic Pakistani".
