OL,4,Cover alleged racist social media posts
OL,6,FSpeaking at a press conference on
OL,7,FThursday, the party leader, Mr Farage,
OL,8,Fsaid: "I discovered this late
OL,9,Fyesterday afternoon and I was slightly
OL,10,Fshocked that there appeared to be a
OL,11,Fsocial media account that had not been
OL,12,Fdeclared to us.
OL,14,F"As part of vetting, people have to be
OL,15,Fhones with us and declare what social
OL,16,Fmedia account they have.
OL,18,F"With candidates, you can deal with
OL,19,Fproblems in their past, but you have
OL,20,Fto know what they are.
